State
> Act like a local variable
> Every Component can have it own state
> any data interaction should happen through state
> With every State Change component will rerender

Props
> Help to transfer data between nested component
> Value of props  will not change it is immutable


var a = [2,4,5,6,8,11,4]
a.map((data) => {return data*2})
[4, 8, 10, 12, 16, 22, 8]

var a = [2,4,5,6,8,11,4]
a.filter((data) => {return data>5})
[6, 8, 11]

